---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t py-12 mt-auto" style="border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76); background: oklch(0.965 0.010 78);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between gap-8">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="max-w-xs">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-5 rounded-sm" style="background: #C9922A;"></span>
          <span class="text-lg font-bold font-display" style="color: oklch(0.20 0.020 243);">Vestara</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.60);">
          Your confident exit from landlord life. Independent educational guidance on DST 1031 exchanges for retiring real estate investors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-3">
        <a href="#guide"
           class="text-sm transition-colors duration-150 hover:opacity-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.60);">DST Starter Guide</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works"
           class="text-sm transition-colors duration-150 hover:opacity-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.60);">How It Works</a>
        <a href="#cta"
           class="text-sm transition-colors duration-150 hover:opacity-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.60);">Get the Guide</a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@vestara.com"
           class="text-sm transition-colors duration-150 hover:opacity-100"
           style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.60);">Contact</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-3"
         style="border-color: oklch(0.92 0.012 76);">
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.40);">
        &copy; {year} Vestara. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs max-w-xl" style="color: oklch(0.28 0.020 240 / 0.40);">
        Vestara is an educational resource only. We are not a registered broker-dealer, investment adviser,
        or attorney. Nothing on this site constitutes investment, tax, or legal advice. Consult a licensed
        professional before making any financial decision.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
